item.title: Medic Girls Thrash UCL
item.author: Elke Wynberg,
item.description: Having lost a match a few days earlier during a freak weather storm in the remote countryside, the ICSM Ladies 1st XI definitely felt we could use a giant dose of good luck when we trooped out to play on Sunday 25 November.
